- Qu'ai-je dis ?

73
00:07:42,461 --> 00:07:45,331
- "Abruti". Dis-le.
- Abruti.

74
00:07:45,765 --> 00:07:47,099
Sans son.

75
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,301
Abruti.

76
00:07:49,502 --> 00:07:52,838
